Class InstructorFeedback

java.lang.Object
  users.InstructorFeedback

public class InstructorFeedback
extends java.lang.Object

Contains which Sections the instructor is assigned to but the instructor does not want to teach, which Sections the instructor cannot teach because the Sections overlap, and whether the instructor is assigned more credit hours than he or she is willing to work.
